Package: tscv
Title: Functions and utilities for time series cross validation and tidy time series forecasting.
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Provides a collection of functions and utilities for time series cross validation and tidy time series forecasting based on the tidyverts (tsibble, fable and fabletools).
Author: Alexander Häußer <alexander-haeusser@gmx.de>
Maintainer: Alexander Häußer <alexander-haeusser@gmx.de>
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.2)
Imports:
    rlang,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    lubridate,
    purrr,
    furrr,
    future,
    tsibble,
    fable,
    fabletools
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
